name: Luster
description: Popular cocktail bar in Mariahilf district (6th district) known for craft cocktails and cozy atmosphere. Features quality drinks in intimate setting with professional mixology.

name: Miles Smiles
description: Small jazz café in Josefstadt district (8th district) named after a Miles Davis album. No-frills jazz pub with live performances and cozy atmosphere. Note: smoking permitted inside.

name: Mon Ami
description: Versatile café, bar and club featuring cocktails, DJ sets, and live acts in cozy living room atmosphere. Has 2 floors with smoking and non-smoking sections. Hosts diverse events including poetry slams, comedy shows, and occasional flea markets.

name: Motto am Fluss
description: Restaurant and bar along the Danube Canal offering views of the water. Serves international cuisine with Austrian focus. Features restaurant, bar, and café areas with different operating hours.

name: Needle Vinyl Club
description: Vinyl record bar featuring blues, jazz and rock'n'roll music. Offers cocktails, wines, and spirits in cozy, intimate atmosphere. Has second location in 6th district.

name: O - The Club
description: Underground club in Albertina Passage next to State Opera, extending over 800m². Features three floors with different music: electronic/house/techno on Fridays, party hits from 90s and charts on Saturdays. Age restrictions: 19+ on Fridays, 21+ on Saturdays.

name: Pitbull Vienna
description: Monthly gay dance party for bears, daddies and admirers held at Club Titanic. Operating since 2009. Features two floors, fetish cabin and darkroom. No dress code. Events typically Saturday from 22:00-06:00.

name: Platzhirsch
description: Club and bar at Opernring in Vienna's first district. Features regular DJ nights and party events. Note: Some sources indicate potential closure - verify current status before visiting.

name: Ponyhof
description: Techno club/bar in 15th district featuring mix of bar and club atmospheres. Was known for super chill techno, electronic, hip hop, and soul music. Note: Club announced closure in July 2025 due to financial struggles - verify current status.

name: Praterstrasse
description: Pizzeria, club and bar in one venue at former TV station location. Features electronic music with clear focus on techno. Located in Leopoldstadt district.
